# Lexsys Project Directory Structure

Registry-first React UI monorepo (pnpm + Turborepo).

```txt
packages/registry → packages/cli → consumer project (user-owned code)
```

**Contracts and rules:** [docs/INDEX.md](../../docs/INDEX.md) — not duplicated here.  
**Agent routing:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md).

Public APIs: `package.json` `exports` only. Never deep-import another package's `src/` or `dist/`.

---

## Repository root

```txt
lexsys/
├── .agents/            # Agent workspace — skills/ (tracked)
├── .cursor/rules/      # Cursor editing behavior (*.mdc)
├── apps/               # playground (smoke), docs (placeholder)
├── docs/               # Hub + reference / operations / contributors
│   ├── reference/      # tokens, ui, registry, cli domain specs
│   ├── operations/     # SCRIPTS, TESTING, DEPLOY, TROUBLESHOOTING
│   └── contributors/   # CONTRIBUTING, STYLE, STYLEGUIDE
├── packages/           # tokens, ui, registry, cli
├── AGENTS.md           # Always-loaded agent routing
├── CONTRIBUTING.md     # Stub → docs/contributors/CONTRIBUTING.md
└── package.json        # Root turbo / pnpm scripts
```

**Ignore for source work:** `node_modules/`, `dist/`, `.turbo/`, `.pnpm-store/`, `.tmp/`

---

## Packages (where to edit)

| Package | Path | Output |
| ------- | ---- | ------ |
| Tokens | `packages/tokens/src/` | `dist/` + generated CSS |
| UI reference | `packages/ui/src/components/{primitives,blocks,templates}/` | `dist/` |
| Registry items | `packages/registry/src/items/` — primitives: auto-scaffolded by `pnpm registry:sync` if missing; **blocks/templates: write manually** | `dist/` + bundled templates |
| Registry templates | `packages/registry/templates/` — **generated by `pnpm registry:sync`, never edit directly** | |
| CLI | `packages/cli/src/` | `dist/` (`lexsys` bin) |

| App | Path | Role |
| --- | ---- | ---- |
| Playground | `apps/playground/` | Maintenance-only monorepo smoke — [TESTING.md](../../docs/operations/TESTING.md#verification-surfaces) |
| Docs site | `apps/docs/` | Placeholder |

---

## Where to change what

| Task | Primary location | Doc |
| ---- | ---------------- | --- |
| Token values / layers | `packages/tokens/src/` | [TOKENS.md](../../docs/reference/tokens/TOKENS.md) |
| Component behavior | `packages/ui/src/components/…` | [UI.md](../../docs/reference/ui/UI.md), [UI_COMPOSITION.md](../../docs/reference/ui/UI_COMPOSITION.md) |
| New registry item metadata | `packages/registry/src/items/<name>.ts` — **always manual** | [REGISTRY.md](../../docs/reference/registry/REGISTRY.md) |
| Registry install templates | Edit `packages/ui/src/components/` → run `pnpm registry:sync` — **never edit `templates/` directly** | `$registry-sync` skill |
| CLI install behavior | `packages/cli/src/` | [CLI.md](../../docs/reference/cli/CLI.md) |
| After UI edits → templates | run `pnpm registry:sync` | `$registry-sync` skill |
| Verification | sandbox + `pnpm *:check` | [TESTING.md](../../docs/operations/TESTING.md) |
| Script names | — | [SCRIPTS.md](../../docs/operations/SCRIPTS.md) only |

Component file shape (all layers):

```txt
ComponentName/
├── ComponentName.tsx
├── ComponentName.types.ts
└── ComponentName.variants.ts
```

